 {
  "i": 105,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Cause of death?"
 },
 {
  "i": 106,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Aim for his right arm!"
 },
 {
  "i": 107,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "This is not Oars' original arm!"
 },
 {
  "i": 108,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Although it was restored by Hogback's amazing skills,"
 },
 {
  "i": 109,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "The joints show remains of terrible frostbite."
 },
 {
  "i": 110,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "I can't tell for sure, but..."
 },
 {
  "i": 111,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "The cause of his death, 500 years ago, was most likely of freezing."
 },
 {
  "i": 112,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Despite being such a monster, he was no match to the forces of nature."
 },
 {
  "i": 113,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "He froze to death as he wandered through the Ice Country."
 },
 {
  "i": 114,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "The reason is that, even five hundred years ago, Oars was still..."
